page_summary: This page provides the table of contents for the CDISC Therapeutic Area User Guide for Breast Cancer, outlining the document structure and major sections such as introduction, overview of breast cancer, subject and disease characteristics, disease management and assessments, analysis data, and appendices. It lists where key topics like diagnosis, staging, pathology, prior treatments, risk factors, treatments, tumor assessment, disease recurrence, analysis endpoints (including PFS, OS, EFS, DFS, DOR, BOR), and datasets are covered in subsequent pages.
